g.text: # ANSI ART GENERATED - Tamagotchi Emotion: Joy
- This creates HIGH CONTRAST / high brightness for a "vivid" (pun on "vivid" + "neon")
- Layers of patterns for depth (nested layers)
- Dense but non-solid, creating a sense of "fluid energy" & "whirl"
- Inspired by 90's rave posters & Tamagotchi design language: small, cute / whimsical, with a tech
- Layered patterns simulate motion, energy flow, and cyberpunk / digital aesthetics.
- Line 1 (#000000 / black BG) ➡ Contrast: #FF0000 "starburst": neon core, hyper-saturated.
- Line 3 (#00BFFF / black BG) ➡ Contrast: #FF00FF (hot neon pink).
• #FF0000 (deep red) = "deep, grounding pulse in the wave"
This pattern evokes tiny, fluttering, cute creatures (in design) combined with "neon energy"
🎉 Let the colors and chaotic yet rhythmic pattern carry you into a flow-state ✌✨"
# LINE 1 - Black background + hot red foreground: "deep grounding"
# LINE 2 - Pink background + white foreground: "pure neon flow"
# LINE 3 - Black background + pink foreground: "contrast for shimmer"
# LINE 4 - Pink background + white foreground: "brightness burst"
# ...repeat pattern, ending on the highest energy, then fading
